24 Section 3. KRS 367.626 is amended to read as follows:
25 (1) As used in this section, "emergency goods or services" means goods, services, or
26 goods and services to immediately respond to a sudden, unexpected occurrence that
27 poses a clear and imminent danger requiring immediate action to prevent or
